c: 11
v: 84
t: "Ne khubandu ba Madyan,(khwaruma) omusiani wabu ( ulangwa mbu) Shuabu. Naboola mbu: “enywe Abandu banje mulaame Nyasaye, mubula Nyasaye wundi owulali ye tawe. Ne Mulaleemia eshichelo nohomba iratili tawe. Esie ebalolanga muli obulayi, ne toto esie abaririra eshinyasio shilibabotokhana inyanga eyo"